MEPC Plc &lt;MEPC.L> said that its offer for&lt;Oldham Estates Ltd> would remain open until further notice.    On February 26 MEPC made an agreed bid for Oldham based ona formula reflecting its asset value at 30 September 1986. Ayear earlier Oldham's net asset value was put at 531.4 mln stg.    As of 1 April the valuation used under the formula hadstill to be agreed so Oldham had yet to give a firmrecommendation to its shareholders regarding the value of thethe offer. REUTER&#3;